1. The input matrix must not be null.
2. The input matrix must have at least one row and one column.
3. The number of rows in the matrix must be equal to the length of the matrix array.
4. The number of columns in each row of the matrix must be equal to the length of the corresponding array in the matrix array.
5. The value of k must be within the range of -10^5 to 10^5.
